4. Updated Java compatibility from 1.8 to 17
5. Replaced discontinued `ffmpeg_kit_flutter_https_gpl` with `ffmpeg_kit_flutter_new_https_gpl`
6. Replaced `image_gallery_saver` with `image_gallery_saver_plus`
